{"tid":2298034,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「石內卜」阿倫歷文日記集結出書　《哈利波特》幕後故事曝光","createTime":"2020-11-23T18:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T12:53:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bb62d79cc6d6f1f6dad6e0320b6133949d95d0","tid":2298034,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"在電影《哈利波特》系列中飾演「石內卜」的英國荷里活男星阿倫歷文（Alan Rickman），4年前因癌症在倫敦家中離世，終年69歲，令全球影迷惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報道，涵蓋了阿倫歷文超過25年的生活和職業生涯的27卷手寫日記，經過整理後將被編輯成一本書，分享包括拍攝《哈利波特》時的幕後故事。<br />\n<br />\n阿倫歷文活躍於幕前近40年，留下不少代表作，當中影迷最深刻的角色，相信少不了《哈利波特》系列的黑魔法防禦術教授石內卜，角色由最初可怕嚴肅、處處針對的反派形象，最終扭轉成為哈利仔的守護者。<br />\n<br />\n現實中的阿倫歷文原來在90年代初開始寫日記，據外媒報道指，他的個人日記集將於2022年正式出版，他在1990年至2016年一直都有保持寫日記的習慣，當中記錄了他在拍攝《哈利波特》的幕後故事、個人想法、拍戲多年的感想、生活上的點滴。<br />\n<br />\n阿倫歷文的日記集被形容將會是睿智、風趣幽默也有八卦的故事，阿倫歷文的遺孀Rima Horton透露老公生前一直想要把日記集結出版，所以才會在26年來都堅持寫日記的習慣。「這本書能展現他真正的模樣，他的幽默感與極高的觀察力，也能感受到他對表演的熱情與執著，大家將能夠看到不只是演員的他，而是一個真實的阿倫歷文。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4424594/org/fc6c6fcea53b645f4f18408be1c9b404.jpg/Y_r0aKHiJLpV-3J1lfT64BAJliJbQawLeqGm8nqhpvI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4424594%2Forg%2Ffc6c6fcea53b645f4f18408be1c9b404.jpg%2FY_r0aKHiJLpV-3J1lfT64BAJliJbQawLeqGm8nqhpvI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3b123bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1492469/org/b3e36f40b83e7c0d20c0ae51589210e0.jpg/wNNW5sfd-INUcNxnWepQSKGLCZ7TyYvbStGeEUrRnhE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1492469%2Forg%2Fb3e36f40b83e7c0d20c0ae51589210e0.jpg%2FwNNW5sfd-INUcNxnWepQSKGLCZ7TyYvbStGeEUrRnhE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2d9ec79c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c519e820d5fd4a0b74bb4124e0a103ba41d581b3","tid":2298034,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b6f5cb2d199583d4a39516f6d639d8c920ad489","tid":2298034,"uid":75050,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T18:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><em><ins><strong>Always.</strong></ins></em></span>"},{"pid":"813544fcc72a73acb793c31e1fa182da8573d9b8","tid":2298034,"uid":17081,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/000/234/885/afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F000%2F234%2F885%2Fafa.jpg&h=d08ae2fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a68bff6cc6d552227eb519aeaa2384102e459bff","tid":2298034,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813544fcc72a73acb793c31e1fa182da8573d9b8","tid":2298034,"uid":17081,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/000/234/885/afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F000%2F234%2F885%2Fafa.jpg&h=d08ae2fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef6d1ff5e68259247d21881b1834c5985d285ae","tid":2298034,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68bff6cc6d552227eb519aeaa2384102e459bff","tid":2298034,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813544fcc72a73acb793c31e1fa182da8573d9b8","tid":2298034,"uid":17081,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/000/234/885/afa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F000%2F234%2F885%2Fafa.jpg&h=d08ae2fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0